Title :- Event Ticket Booking System

Description :-
This SQL project simulates an online event ticket booking system. It includes user management, event details, venues, seat assignments, ticket generation, and payments.

Tools Used :-
- MySQL Workbench

ER Diagram :-
Entities :
- `User`
- `Venue`
- `Event`
- `Seat`
- `Booking`
- `Ticket`
- `Payment`

Relationships :-
- A User books multiple tickets.
- An Event takes place at a Venue.
- Seats are assigned per Event.
- A Booking is linked to Seats and Payment.

SQL Script Includes :-
- Database and table creation
- Foreign keys and constraints
- Use of `AUTO_INCREMENT`, boolean flags
- Normalized to 3NF

